{
  "info": {
    "name": "CleanArchitecture api/{{apiVersion}}",
    "_postman_id": "c1ea0a17-0000-4000-8000-cleanarch0001",
    "description": "ASP.NET Core 9 Clean Architecture sample api/{{apiVersion}}.\n\n## Setup\n1. Run the api/{{apiVersion}}: `dotnet run --project src/CleanArchitecture.api/{{apiVersion}}` (listens on https://localhost:5001 / http://localhost:5000).\n2. Import this collection. The `baseUrl` collection variable defaults to https://localhost:5001 — change it, or import the bundled environment file, to switch hosts.\n3. The dev cert is self-signed. In Postman: Settings → General → turn **SSL certificate verification** OFF (or use the http://localhost:5000 base URL).\n\n## Chaining\nThe **Create Product**, **Create Order**, and **Place Order** requests capture the returned `id` into the `productId` / `orderId` collection variables, so the GET/PUT/DELETE/cancel/confirm requests work right after without manual copy-paste.\n\n## Error mapping\n- FluentValidation failures → 400 (ValidationException)\n- Domain invariant violations → 400 (DomainException)\n- Missing entity → 404 (NotFoundException)\nAll mapped by `api/{{apiVersion}}ExceptionFilter` to ProblemDetails.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Products",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Products",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products?page=1&pageSize=20",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api/{{apiVersion}}", "Products"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "pageSize", "value": "20" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Paged list of products. Returns PagedResult<ProductDto>."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Product By Id",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api/{{apiVersion}}", "Products", "{{productId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Returns a single ProductDto. 404 if not found."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Product",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (body && body.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('productId', body.id);",
                  "        console.log('Saved productId =', body.id);",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Mechanical Keyboard\",\n  \"description\": \"87-key hot-swappable, brown switches\",\n  \"price\": 129.99,\n  \"stock\": 50\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api/{{apiVersion}}", "Products"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a product. Returns 201 with the created ProductDto. Captures `id` into the productId variable."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"id\": \"{{productId}}\",\n  \"name\": \"Mechanical Keyboard (v2)\",\n  \"description\": \"87-key hot-swappable, silent red switches\",\n  \"price\": 139.99,\n  \"stock\": 42\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api/{{apiVersion}}", "Products", "{{productId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Updates a product. The route id must match the body id (else 400). Returns 204 No Content."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/Products/{{productId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api/{{apiVersion}}", "Products", "{{productId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Deletes a product. Returns 204 No Content. 404 if not found."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
